{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bg":"black","nameNarration":"","narration":"Chapter 7@\"Connecting Feelings\"","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":37.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21184.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime08","chara":[{"id":831303,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Oh..."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"I became a Magical Girl, didn't I?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"That's right."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Your wish was granted."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"If you break this mirror, the world of the red moon@will vanish,"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"and Perenelle, Kagome, and the others will return@to their original world."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"They will return to their normal lives as if nothing@happened."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"The rebellion planned by Dauphin Louis should@also come to an end somehow."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Yeah, that's great!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Huh...? What about this cool-looking pen...?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"It seems like a brand-new pen created by your wish."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"I knew it...! Just as I thought!"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Qube, does this place connect to the future?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"According to what Kagome Satori said, yes."},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"In that case, in the dreams of"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Kagome from \"before she came to the Ark\","},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"I could secretly deliver her this pen!"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"...I see, so that's what you mean."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"It's not that Kagome Satori was chosen"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"because she had a magic pen..."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"But the fact that she had a magic pen at all,"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"that itself is the result of your wish, Torte."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Exactly!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"And because I wished for the feelings of La Pucelle"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"to be rightfully passed down,"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"what Kagome recorded with the magic pen"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"became the truth."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"The order of cause and effect was reversed,@it seems..."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"The mystery remains unsolved until the end."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21184.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story05","chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Well, let's do what we need to do...and then,@return to our original time!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"First, deliver the pen to Kagome Satori"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"from before she came to the past."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":200}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","visible":"hide"}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Then, I will destroy the mirror."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"To deliver the pen...how should I do it...?"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21184.jpg","nameNarration":"","narration":"[surround:7010_bell]*Dong*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21184.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":831303,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"...?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"The sound of a bell..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"flashEffect":"explosion","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":831303,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"...!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"flashEffect":"explosion","se":"3205_charm","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21372.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102003,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":1.5},{"chara":[{"id":102003,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.5},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"white","surround":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Torte","narration":"[textBlack:\"... Kagome, can you hear me? It's me, Torte.\"]","narrationBg":"white","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","surround":"7202_telepathy","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"[textBlack:\"Once I destroy the mirror@and the world returns to normal,@it'll be like all of our journeys@together never happened.\"]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:\"When you next wake up, Kagome,@you'll forget everything.\"]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:\"But you know, I want the feelings of La Pucelle@to live forever in your heart...@That's what I wish.\"]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:\"...So please.\"]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:\"Don't treat her feelings as if they never existed.\"]"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out","surround":"stop","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":2.5},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"se":"3214_ban"}]},"version":3}
